{"tid":2406230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"童星Celine齊貼相拜年「小巨肺」眼妝出事 「美心妹妹」齊蔭look少女味濃","createTime":"2021-02-13T04:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T03:00:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0022534f6a0177c12a6bd0b9fd3286fe6dd4e309","tid":2406230,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:40:47.000Z","msg":"同樣叫Celine，同樣在童年時甫出道一鳴驚人，一個Celine叫譚芷昀，今年13歲，9歲時在美國真人騷《全美一叮》，憑一曲《My Heart Will Go On》衝出香港，被稱為「小巨肺」的她，當年在YouTube上載其表演片段，短短6日，便有6,000萬瀏覽人次。至於另一位Celine妹妹楊鎧凝，當年一個賀年蘿蔔糕廣告，旋即被稱為「美心妹妹」，可愛精靈冬菇look至今令人難忘。今年12歲的她，和「小巨肺」Celine同樣愛在IG分享近況，日前二人趁新年，亦有貼新相同大家拜年。<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CxRv9iwYZjIlRkpeRMztl8stpuY=/748x748/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XPKABU55HVBSNKS3GDKCUHBU3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCxRv9iwYZjIlRkpeRMztl8stpuY%3D%2F748x748%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXPKABU55HVBSNKS3GDKCUHBU3E.jpg&h=dcc9ead0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xpFHBDHWINIRwWtWW9hHGbIcYgU=/1080x1350/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RGOXGFYJDJBJ3G22BJCKGUYDD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxpFHBDHWINIRwWtWW9hHGbIcYgU%3D%2F1080x1350%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRGOXGFYJDJBJ3G22BJCKGUYDD4.jpg&h=b549e779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/La_LURzB7HYNbRFhrU5Zpge9iPk=/1193x963/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DULFT4B4JGIZDEDAK4MEZLL64.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLa_LURzB7HYNbRFhrU5Zpge9iPk%3D%2F1193x963%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast